</FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Segoe UI, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=4><U><B>readest</B></U></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Segoe UI, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=4>
</FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Segoe UI, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=4><U><B>thou</B></U></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Segoe UI, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=4>?</FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS="western"><FONT COLOR="#000000">&nbsp;</FONT></P>
<P CLASS="western"><FONT COLOR="#001d35"><FONT FACE="Google Sans"><FONT SIZE=4>Peter
in 1 Peter 2[:9] says, &quot;You are a royal priesthood and a
priestly kingdom,&quot; and Revelation [5:10], &quot;Through your
